  "text": "To relate the singularities of more general orbit closuresΩ (λ ′ ,µ ′ ) to the singularities of orbits in the enhanced nilpotent cones (for different groups GL n , n = N ) we need a certain generalization of Lusztig's construction, due to Mirković and Vybornov [CITATION_1] .",
